oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tennessee Telluride at the Belmont
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: fund raising; Bush, Sam, 1952-; Douglas, Jerry, 1956-; Harris, Emmylou; Randall, Jon;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing Tennessee Telluride with Sam Bush, Jerry Douglas, Emmylou Harris, Byron House and Jon Randall at the Belmont University's Troutt and Theater on December 12. Event benefits the Epilepsy Foundation in Middle and West Tennessee.
